These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-1-1::.
7 different pets are kept: goldfish, cat, guinea-pig, snake, ferret, chinchilla, bird
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: animation, action, superhero, guinea-pigsy, mystery, scientific, musical
The people have 7 different jobs:  nurse, doctor, architect, bartender, engineer, police-officer, accountant
There are 7 different favourite colors: amber, chestnut, white, blue, pink, emerald, grey
 1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 2. the person watching guinea-pigsy movies is on the right of the nurse##1
 3. the person who likes amber is the engineer##1
 4. the engineer is on the right of the doctor##1
 5. the person watching musical movies is on the far left##1
 6. the person who likes white is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 7. the person watching action movies is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 8. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 9. the person watching superhero movies is on the far right##1
10. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
11. the owner of the chinchilla is in the middle##1
12. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left##1
13. the person watching mystery movies is in the middle##1
14. the police-officer is on the left of the architect##1
15. the person who likes grey is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
16. the engineer is on the left of the police-officer##1
17. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
18. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the bartender##1
19. the person who likes white is in the middle##1
20. the bartender is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
21. the person watching action movies is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |    5     |     6      |       7       |
| Pet      | guinea-pig    | goldfish     | bird  | chinchilla   | snake | ferret      | cat          |
| Movie-Genre   | musical    | guinea-pigsy   | scientific  | mystery       | animation  | action      | superhero     |
| Job         | nurse | doctor | engineer | police-officer | architect   | bartender     | accountant |
| Color     | grey      | emerald   | amber   | white  | blue  | pink | chestnut       |

